{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|1Co|13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","chapter":13,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v11","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:13:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":13,"verse":1,"text":"If I speak human or angelic tongues but do not have love, I am a noisy gong or a clanging cymbal.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:13:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":13,"verse":2,"text":"If I have the gift of prophecy and understand all mysteries and all knowledge, and if I have all faith so that I can move mountains but do not have love, I am nothing.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:13:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":13,"verse":3,"text":"And if I give away all my possessions, and if I give over my body in order to boast but do not have love, I gain nothing.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:13:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":13,"verse":4,"text":"Love is patient, love is kind. Love does not envy, is not boastful, is not arrogant,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:13:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":13,"verse":5,"text":"is not rude, is not self-seeking, is not irritable, and does not keep a record of wrongs.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:13:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":13,"verse":6,"text":"Love finds no joy in unrighteousness but rejoices in the truth.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:13:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":13,"verse":7,"text":"It bears all things, believes all things, hopes all things, endures all things.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:13:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":13,"verse":8,"text":"Love never ends. But as for prophecies, they will come to an end; as for tongues, they will cease; as for knowledge, it will come to an end.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:13:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":13,"verse":9,"text":"For we know in part, and we prophesy in part,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:13:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":13,"verse":10,"text":"but when the perfect comes, the partial will come to an end.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:13:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":13,"verse":11,"text":"When I was a child, I spoke like a child, I thought like a child, I reasoned like a child. When I became a man, I put aside childish things.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:13:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":13,"verse":12,"text":"For now we see only a reflection as in a mirror, but then face to face. Now I know in part, but then I will know fully, as I am fully known.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:13:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","bookOrder":45,"chapter":13,"verse":13,"text":"Now these three remain: faith, hope, and love —but the greatest of these is love.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"}],"layout":{"bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Co","chapter":13,"paragraphStarts":[1,4,8],"headings":[{"beforeVerse":1,"text":"Love: The Superior Way"}],"poetryBlocks":[],"studyByVerse":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:13:1","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"If I speak human or angelic tongues "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"languages, also in v. 8"},{"kind":"text","text":" but do not have love, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 13:35","book":"Jhn","chapter":13,"verse":35,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 4:7–12","book":"1Jn","chapter":4,"verse":7,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" I am a noisy gong "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 10:9","book":"Mat","chapter":10,"verse":9,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" or a clanging cymbal. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jn 13:35","book":"Jhn","chapter":13,"verse":35},{"label":"1Jn 4:7–12","book":"1Jn","chapter":4,"verse":7},{"label":"Mt 10:9","book":"Mat","chapter":10,"verse":9}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"languages, also in v. 8"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Co:13:2","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"If I have the gift of prophecy "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 14:1","book":"1Co","chapter":14,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 14:3","book":"1Co","chapter":14,"verse":3,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 14:22","book":"1Co","chapter":14,"verse":22,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 4:11","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":11,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 5:20","book":"1Th","chapter":5,"verse":20,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" and understand all mysteries and all knowledge, and if I have all faith so that I can move mountains "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 17:20","book":"Mat","chapter":17,"verse":20,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" but do not have love, I am nothing. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Co 14:1","book":"1Co","chapter":14,"verse":1},{"label":"1Co 14:3","book":"1Co","chapter":14,"verse":3},{"label":"1Co 14:22","book":"1Co","chapter":14,"verse":22},{"label":"Eph 4:11","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":11},{"label":"1Th 5:20","book":"1Th","chapter":5,"verse":20},{"label":"Mt 17:20","book":"Mat","chapter":17,"verse":20}],"footnotes":